@startuml Booking_Saga_StateMachine
title Booking Saga - Машина состояний

[*] --> CREATED : Пассажир создал заказ

CREATED --> FRAUD_CHECK : CheckBookingFraudCmd

FRAUD_CHECK --> CALCULATING_PRICE : FraudCheckPassed
FRAUD_CHECK --> CANCELLED : FraudDetected [компенсация: CancelBookingCmd]

CALCULATING_PRICE --> CALCULATING_ROUTE : PriceCalculated
CALCULATING_PRICE --> CANCELLED : PriceError [компенсация: CancelBookingCmd]

CALCULATING_ROUTE --> MATCHING_DRIVER : RouteCalculated
CALCULATING_ROUTE --> CANCELLED : RouteError [компенсация: CancelBookingCmd]

MATCHING_DRIVER --> CONFIRMED : DriverAssigned + NotifyPartiesCmd
MATCHING_DRIVER --> MATCHING_DRIVER : DriverNotFound [retry до 3 раз с расширением радиуса]
MATCHING_DRIVER --> CANCELLED : Все попытки исчерпаны [компенсация: CancelBookingCmd]
MATCHING_DRIVER --> MATCHING_DRIVER : DriverCancelled [ReleaseDriverCmd + retry]

CONFIRMED --> [*]

CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of CANCELLED
  Причины отмены:
  - CANCELLED_FRAUD
  - CANCELLED_NO_DRIVER
  - CANCELLED_TIMEOUT
  - CANCELLED_BY_PASSENGER
end note

note right of MATCHING_DRIVER
  Таймаут шага: 30 сек
  Таймаут саги: 60 сек
end note

@enduml
